<span id="freeTextContainer12331434875758247802">The path to spiritual enlightenment... is definitely NOT found in this book, but you will get a few laughs along the way. It has a kind of lopsided approach that is rather different and that is what kept me reading. Not much of what you expect in here and not a book easy to describe. Some things that happen are unfortunate and untimely, but the twist her best friend puts on things will get you thinking. A few parts didn&apos;t quite pan out or get explained like I imagined it hoped, but it was cute a</span>
  <span id="freeText12331434875758247802" style="display:none">The path to spiritual enlightenment... is definitely NOT found in this book, but you will get a few laughs along the way. It has a kind of lopsided approach that is rather different and that is what kept me reading. Not much of what you expect in here and not a book easy to describe. Some things that happen are unfortunate and untimely, but the twist her best friend puts on things will get you thinking. A few parts didn't quite pan out or get explained like I imagined it hoped, but it was cute and original.<br /><br />ARC provided in exchange for honest review.</span>
