        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1435804962" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10781472298299116553">I loved this book! It starts out fairly light. Two women friends decide to help other women who are in bad relationships. Then it turns a bit scary! This is a really good read, and I loved that my hometown of Sacramento is mentioned. I received a free copy of this book in exchange for an honest review - and I&apos;m so glad I did.</span>
