<span id="freeTextContainer16381224099441991524">Tara was a jilted lover after realizing her boyfriend was cheating on her. She didn’t have a good track record for picking out good men. In fact, she was done with them.<br/><br/>Her friend was the alpha female and a bisexual fiend, and she urges her to forget about men but not about sex.<br/><br/>But then the cheating bastard dies—the third boyfriend to drop dead. Coincidence? Or was the universe at play here? What the heck were these broads talking about? Was Tara bad luck? Was she a grim reaper? What? This wasn’</span>
  <span id="freeText16381224099441991524" style="display:none">Tara was a jilted lover after realizing her boyfriend was cheating on her. She didn’t have a good track record for picking out good men. In fact, she was done with them.<br /><br />Her friend was the alpha female and a bisexual fiend, and she urges her to forget about men but not about sex.<br /><br />But then the cheating bastard dies—the third boyfriend to drop dead. Coincidence? Or was the universe at play here? What the heck were these broads talking about? Was Tara bad luck? Was she a grim reaper? What? This wasn’t making sense to me. </span>
